    "Additionally, datasets may contain substantial errors arising from their researchers' lack of expertise.",
    "Moreover, human curators may not always control annotations, and some may be incorrect.",
    "Further, annotations on comparable genes from various laboratories or biological research groups may differ and contain conflicting data.",
    "Such challenges can potentially impact the efficacy of an ML mechanism application.",
